item.title: Compiler error what should i do?
item.dc:creator: @The_cook_from_runesc The cook from runescape
item.description:
@The_cook_from_runesc wrote:

[quote=“Fat Cookies, post:4, topic:280190”][quote author=cowbell link=topic=370144.msg2803452#msg2803452 date=1243577060]
how? i already done public int inCastleWars()
is that right?^

[/quote]
public void inCastleWars();

Thats what a method should start off with.[/quote]

Why? If it’s a void it won’t return anything so what use is it in an if statement?

You were right to use public int inCastleWars() but there must be something wrong with how or where you’re initializing the method. I’m not sure if it matters, but make sure it’s before the if statement and actually in the client class.

Post your method here.
